  "description": "**Milestone:** Phase 2: Component Expansion\n\nCreate a Tailwind CSS preset that maps Helix design tokens to Tailwind utility classes. Consumers install the preset and get Helix-aligned colors, spacing, typography, and shadows in their Tailwind projects.\n\n**Files to Modify:**\n- packages/tailwind-preset/\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] Tailwind preset package published as @helixds/tailwind-preset\n- [ ] Colors map to --hx-color-* tokens\n- [ ] Spacing maps to --hx-spacing-* tokens\n- [ ] Typography maps to --hx-font-* tokens\n- [ ] Dark mode support via data-theme attribute\n- [ ] Documentation with usage examples\n\n**Complexity:** medium",
